::The Galactors::

The Galactors continue to fly away from the ship, circling up and 
avoiding most of the shots. The missiles wern't a problem, but the 
laser shots were a bit annoying. The jets fly back over the base, 
spinning to avoid missiles and firing several shots down at the 
shields.
